snippet.title: Soul Keeper | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
#indie #soulkeeper #games 
📌 Soul Keeper! Story based platform game. Sometimes it will drive you crazy with its difficulty, but it will drag you along with its story. Overcome obstacles, pass levels and collect the story!

📢 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2524590/Soul_Keeper/

👉🏻 Add to your wish list and stay tuned! #indiegame 

The story is about fantastic fictional characters, fantasy fictional worlds and an intruder who wanders between these worlds. Felis, the protector of the spirit realm, travels to a different realm to follow the souls he thinks have escaped, and completely different events develop.
